    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><img alt="" class="left" src="https://association.drupal.org/files/12020029326_7d54e40ba5_z.jpg" />If Drupal adoption is going to increase, we’ll need to grow the community— and that means continuing to bring developers, web designers, and digital experts into the Drupal fold. For the finale of our series on Drupal training options, we spoke to several of the many experts in Drupal training, and wanted to share their thoughts with the community.</p>
<p>When it comes to increasing the amount of Drupal talent in the market, there are more options to learn the platform than ever before.</p></div></div></div>
